{"tid":1708984,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"11.12 九龍塘教育局人鏈要人","createTime":"2019-11-11T18:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:46:42.000Z","uid":319057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12f9313d28e47e3bdd527ffc45e1f0c08e01c949","tid":1708984,"uid":319057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中學生反打壓爭取停課人鏈<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信聽日罷工罷課都好「得閒」㗎啦<br />\n朝早發完夢，食完飯晏晝安排咗活動俾大家<br />\n<br />\n16:30 九龍塘教育服務中心集合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnMhwCP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnMhwCP.png&h=66548144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家得閑咪喺九龍塘地鐵站接放工，到時好多人㗎。個個都要放工返屋企食飯，千祈唔好阻人收工"},{"pid":"dcf085ab83625cc4b14a6349e4db5a23a64832af","tid":1708984,"uid":323113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:57:34.000Z","msg":"幫你手動推"},{"pid":"ba7cc2003a5eacc7408136d4feed2d62315fc5be","tid":1708984,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:04:25.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1918c0f0b844019f57c32425888a6f33f3015c2c","tid":1708984,"uid":200315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}